Bayer Says CropScience Unit Buys Raps GbR Oilseed Rape Business

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-10-07T12:04:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/bayer-says-cropscience-unit-buys-raps-gbr-oilseed-rape-business.html
Bayer AG (BAYN) ’s CropScience division
completed the acquisition of the oilseed rape business of German
seed company Raps GbR to strengthen its oilseed rape breeding
activities, the company said in an e-mailed statement today. The
company didn’t disclose financial details of the transaction.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
